    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Continuously Cycle: </text>the <text styleclass="VariableName">Master-Machine-Angle</text> (<text styleclass="VariableName">MMA)</text> increases at a constant rate from 0 to 360, again, and again. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Step Forward</text><text styleclass="T_Menu">&#32;</text>or <text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Step Backward</text> : increment the <text styleclass="VariableName">MMA</text> by<text styleclass="T_Menu"> 360°/ </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Machine-Settings">Number-of-Steps</link><text styleclass="Parameter">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Home (ALT+H)</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> : moves the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">MMA</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> and </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Revs</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> to </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Zero</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> (0)</text></para>
